metadata.name: boy_#098
metadata.description:
Our first irl event in Nagoya Japan on 19th February 2023 DX RAINBOW FESTIVAL.
In order to accelerate society into the unseen future, it was launched as an event that will trigger the creation of an exciting future. 
The theme is to create an opportunity to deepen the connection with family, friends, and society by comparing NFT to the rainbow. 
Through this event, we will provide special moments with family and friends who are dear to you that are a little different from usual and lead to our future.
